			 seq.</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity>is amended by inserting after<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Reclamation Wastewater and Groundwater Study and Facilities Act/s:1656">section 1656</cato:entity-ref>the
			 following:</text>
        <quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HECB7410DEBA544D2AB55B140E83C04A7" style="OLC">
          <section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HEA18162D72E14964B7CB19B2F8C44F62" section-type="subsequent-section">
            <enum>1657.</enum>
            <header display-inline="yes-display-inline">City of Hermiston, Oregon, water recycling
				and reuse project</header>
            <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H2F144A9CDAF245BFAD469587F1A52606">
              <enum>(a)</enum>
              <header display-inline="yes-display-inline">Authorization</header>
              <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="1400">Secretary</cato:entity-ref>, in cooperation with the City
				of Hermiston, Oregon, is authorized to participate in the design, planning, and
				construction of permanent facilities to reclaim and reuse water in the City of
				Hermiston, Oregon.</text>
            </subsection>
            <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H89890DBC729A41BEAE97FC0055ECD700">
              <enum>(b)</enum>
              <header display-inline="yes-display-inline">Cost share</header>
              <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The Federal share of the costs of the project described
				in<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Reclamation Wastewater and Groundwater Study and Facilities Act/s:61_/ss:a" proposed="true">subsection (a)</cato:entity-ref>shall not exceed 25 percent of the total cost.</text>
            </subsection>
            <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="HEA53788F44904208B12DCC06D411A5A0">
              <enum>(c)</enum>
              <header display-inline="yes-display-inline">Limitation</header>
              <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" entity-id="1400">Secretary</cato:entity-ref>shall not provide funds for
				the operation and maintenance of the project described in<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Reclamation Wastewater and Groundwater Study and Facilities Act/s:1657/ss:a" proposed="true">subsection
				(a)</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
            </subsection>
          </section>
          <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
        </quoted-block>
